{"tid":2183680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：正式批鬥醫管局員工陣線","createTime":"2020-09-01T05:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T09:28:54.000Z","uid":240256,"like":335,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"bd16157382f730cf08ff34253f11d2882ade2242","tid":2183680,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:32:58.000Z","msg":"林鄭今朝開名逐點反駁醫管局員工陣線，總之都係講嚟講去三幅被，話封關只係口號，不切實際，但係就明知第三波疫情係源自豁免檢疫人士；又話咩一直希望盡量保留市民人身自由，但係俾人檢測又唔俾人投票；仲話最愛護醫管局員工，但又諗住削減醫管局撥款。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\">敵人嘅敵人就係朋友。林鄭今次擺明針對醫管局員工陣線，唔該大家繼續支持佢哋同埋醫護手足：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n1. Follow 佢哋：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107732697364538/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107732697364538%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7gy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=338c6d3d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107732697364538/</a><br />\n<br />\n2. Share/like佢哋被林鄭批鬥嘅post：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/107732697364538/posts/195674495237024/?extid=c9zORIutldm4bjFU&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F107732697364538%2Fposts%2F195674495237024%2F%3Fextid%3Dc9zORIutldm4bjFU%26d%3Dn&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7gy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=651d0eb0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/107732697364538/posts/195674495237024/?extid=c9zORIutldm4bjFU&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 繼續杯葛全民檢疫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHDBNcc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHDBNcc.jpg&h=bcf616d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fea4767b16dea6a42c9f988258eb7d6d8adf963c","tid":2183680,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c88bd10238498f3e6e4ee95285439eb10e2091a0","tid":2183680,"uid":240256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T05:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i